{"tid":2311214,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有無巴打同我一樣好僧自己女朋友行街","createTime":"2020-12-04T01:36:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-04T06:03:26.000Z","uid":370062,"like":3,"dislike":32,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"0635ba8392badaf69002d022eeff228685f5743b","tid":2311214,"uid":370062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T01:36:14.000Z","msg":"我同我女朋友一齊左幾年  <br />\n咁大家會比對方有私人時間 而佢大部份既時間就係同佢班朋友行街<br />\n我覺得行街真係無問題 <br />\n<br />\n自從十月之後 我覺得佢變左另一個人咁  <br />\n每個星期五六日 佢都好少同我出街 同我講呢排唔得閒 好忙  <br />\n初時我都覺得無問題 我以為係佢計劃緊我地既將來 去進修下自己<br />\n但係十一月到而家 佢每一次星期六日都同我講 好忙 唔肯同我見下面<br />\n<br />\n直到有一個星期六 我女朋友好似知錯咁 約我星期六上佢屋企....<br />\n我上到佢屋企果陣 我只係見到成屋都係新衫<br />\n<br />\n我即刻忍唔住問 你咁多個星期六日就係行街買咗咁多衫？<br />\n佢好唔耐煩咁答我 呢個係咩只有五六日先買到  仲叫我claim返錢俾佢先<br />\n我果陣真係好嬲 你為左買衫 買到全日去行街 仲要我俾錢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但果一刻 我無出一粒聲<br />\n因為係堆衫面前既佢 完全變左另一個人咁 我呢幾年從來都無見過佢為咗買衫而發咁大脾氣<br />\n<br />\n佢每一件都係着咗一次就冇掂過 成日又去行街  成日又買新衫 <br />\n呢件唔襯我對鞋呀/ 呢件同隔離陳師奶撞款呀/點解你啲taste咁差㗎<br />\n買左衫之後我見到佢激動到 大力攞走我銀包啲錢  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n果刻 我嚇到講唔到野 我屋企人都未試過攞我咁多錢.... 佢買衫真係好恐怖<br />\n<br />\n一齊幾年都未見過佢咁嬲既樣..... <br />\n我事後問返佢朋友 話平時同佢買衫唔係咁...仲有講有笑.....<br />\n到底點解會咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"216513be427db259fc4831f24d8d2fb706e55f20","tid":2311214,"uid":149611,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T01:37:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ed1f0dae5f65c1219841cdc1832315932f97db0","tid":2311214,"uid":370062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"216513be427db259fc4831f24d8d2fb706e55f20","tid":2311214,"uid":149611,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T01:37:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T01:37:51.000Z","msg":"hi嘟嘟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"680e7fa5d21e17021f3d26483a1c21b8b959893e","tid":2311214,"uid":19493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T01:38:36.000Z","msg":"分啦on9"},{"pid":"8e1e8d071a389b3d2f80a797fed38cdfc586093b","tid":2311214,"uid":225698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T01:38:48.000Z","msg":"可能呢個先係本來嘅佢<br />\n又或者人大左 搵錢多左<br />\n想買自己鍾意嘅嘢姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1a273676260fd6e47659cdd97185ec62b90fca6","tid":2311214,"uid":370062,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"8e1e8d071a389b3d2f80a797fed38cdfc586093b","tid":2311214,"uid":225698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T01:38:48.000Z","msg":"可能呢個先係本來嘅佢<br />\n又或者人大左 搵錢多左<br />\n想買自己鍾意嘅嘢姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T01:39:53.000Z","msg":"啲衫多到我要踩住佢啲衫先行到路<br />\n仲有點解要用我啲錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgm